1
00:00:03,110 --> 00:00:07,110
<font size="20"><font face="Trebuchet MS"><b>{\an7}Strongest Because of Imperfection</b></font></font>

2
00:00:11,980 --> 00:00:13,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So they survived.</font>

3
00:00:14,430 --> 00:00:16,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a persistent lot.</font>

4
00:00:17,430 --> 00:00:20,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They're after the new Diva.</i></font>

5
00:00:20,820 --> 00:00:23,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They won't have an emotional 
reunion on my watch.</i></font>

6
00:00:24,690 --> 00:00:26,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chill out a bit, Apollo.</font>

7
00:00:27,270 --> 00:00:29,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me take care of them this time.</font>

8
00:00:31,740 --> 00:00:36,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for leading them here, Medea.</font>

9
00:00:37,140 --> 00:00:38,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is rare.</i></font>

10
00:00:38,990 --> 00:00:42,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You've always preferred to be in 
the shadows, outwitting the enemy.</i></font>

11
00:00:42,750 --> 00:00:45,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I could use some exercise.</font>

12
00:00:46,600 --> 00:00:50,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In exchange, I want to ask you a favor.</font>

13
00:00:59,460 --> 00:01:01,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Mirage appeared 
simultaneously in 25 locations.</font>

14
00:01:01,500 --> 00:01:02,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not to mention...</font>

15
00:01:02,580 --> 00:01:05,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're all political hubs.</font>

16
00:01:05,100 --> 00:01:07,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no logic 
in setting targets like this.</font>

17
00:01:07,930 --> 00:01:12,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's an attack solely to put 
the whole Earth in chaos.</font>

18
00:01:12,880 --> 00:01:15,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who knew they'd be the one 
to give us a signal?</font>

19
00:01:15,970 --> 00:01:18,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. They don't care
about the consequences.</font>

20
00:01:19,440 --> 00:01:24,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which means our kids 
are closing in on Nagi.</font>

21
00:01:24,980 --> 00:01:28,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now this is a race, SI-VIS.</font>

22
00:01:28,980 --> 00:01:33,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you take me down first
or does Earth perish before that?</font>

23
00:01:35,160 --> 00:01:37,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ready, set... go!</font>

24
00:01:38,490 --> 00:01:42,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}A calling arises from deep 
within in my burning heart</i></font>

25
00:01:43,490 --> 00:01:45,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}It's Show Time</i></font>

26
00:01:54,260 --> 00:01:57,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The price of living in the time of freedom</i></font>

27
00:01:57,250 --> 00:01:58,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}"So, what do you want to do?"</i></font>

28
00:01:58,860 --> 00:02:04,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Just standing there with my empty body</i></font>

29
00:02:04,500 --> 00:02:08,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Like a calling to protect the world</i></font>

30
00:02:08,990 --> 00:02:15,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I craved an unequaled gift</i></font>

31
00:02:15,390 --> 00:02:18,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Lost in night's darkness</i></font>

32
00:02:18,490 --> 00:02:22,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Until a voice called out to me</i></font>

33
00:02:22,220 --> 00:02:25,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Like the light that declares the dawn</i></font>

34
00:02:26,340 --> 00:02:31,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I'll take you with me at 
any cost (I pray and wish)</i></font>

35
00:02:29,510 --> 00:02:34,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Beyond the Echo-verse (To the future)</i></font>

36
00:02:32,580 --> 00:02:35,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Just being with you makes me strong</i></font>

37
00:02:35,340 --> 00:02:36,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}It's not an exaggeration</i></font>

38
00:02:36,720 --> 00:02:41,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}That encounter was a supernova 
(Our eyes were locked)</i></font>

39
00:02:39,350 --> 00:02:44,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In an instant, everything that I am 
(In an instant)</i></font>

40
00:02:42,710 --> 00:02:48,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Will be changed forever (Just to be)</i></font>

41
00:02:46,650 --> 00:02:50,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A calling arises from deep
 within in my burning heart</i></font>

42
00:02:50,490 --> 00:02:52,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Destiny is Calling us now</i></font>

43
00:02:52,950 --> 00:02:55,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Just to be who we are</i></font>

44
00:02:55,530 --> 00:02:58,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Destiny is Calling us now</i></font>

45
00:02:58,070 --> 00:03:00,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Just to be by your side</i></font>

46
00:03:11,710 --> 00:03:13,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Everyone, can you hear me?</i></font>

47
00:03:13,410 --> 00:03:14,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Loud and clear.</font>

48
00:03:14,610 --> 00:03:17,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, wow! How are you doing this?</font>

49
00:03:17,090 --> 00:03:20,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Connecting Harmonia and 
myself through Metis.</font>

50
00:03:20,970 --> 00:03:24,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I didn't think Earth technology 
was capable of this.</i></font>

51
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:28,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not Earth technology. 
It's <i>my</i> skill.</font>

52
00:03:28,290 --> 00:03:31,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now we're ready for the live concert.</font>

53
00:03:31,080 --> 00:03:34,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But we can't tell what's really 
going on over there.</font>

54
00:03:34,530 --> 00:03:39,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you're the stage director 
of SI-VIS today, Medea.</font>

55
00:03:44,630 --> 00:03:46,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I always do my best.</font>

56
00:03:47,350 --> 00:03:49,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So the rest is up to SI-VIS.</font>

57
00:03:49,160 --> 00:03:50,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So cold!</font>

58
00:03:50,410 --> 00:03:54,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you say something that will, 
I don't know, boost our morale?</font>

59
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:59,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which makes you, Rui, 
the supervisor for today.</font>

60
00:03:59,860 --> 00:04:03,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Work with her and
 lead the concert to success.</font>

61
00:04:03,710 --> 00:04:06,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you sure you can trust her that much?</font>

62
00:04:07,590 --> 00:04:11,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shouldn't you trust her more than anyone?</font>

63
00:04:11,590 --> 00:04:13,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As women who loved the same man.</font>

64
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:17,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can sympathize with her, can't you?</font>

65
00:04:21,870 --> 00:04:23,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">According to Harmonia headquarters,</font>

66
00:04:23,770 --> 00:04:27,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we have about thirty minutes
before the Mirages close.</font>

67
00:04:27,740 --> 00:04:31,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have to rescue the Diva 
before that and stop the Mirages.</font>

68
00:04:32,250 --> 00:04:33,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a race against time.</font>

69
00:04:33,630 --> 00:04:37,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You say that, but will saving Nagi 
really stop the Mirages?</font>

70
00:04:37,760 --> 00:04:40,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The situation on Earth
must be dealt with,</font>

71
00:04:40,100 --> 00:04:42,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but rushing into things 
just to fail won't help.</font>

72
00:04:42,260 --> 00:04:46,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, we should take our chances 
with the time limit of thirty minutes.</font>

73
00:04:46,900 --> 00:04:51,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because that man is most likely 
playing games with you.</font>

74
00:04:54,760 --> 00:04:58,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on. Come on. Come on!</font>

75
00:04:59,230 --> 00:05:02,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will reunite you guys.</font>

76
00:05:02,440 --> 00:05:07,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just like Romeo and
Juliet on your planet.</font>

77
00:05:08,380 --> 00:05:09,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that...?</font>

78
00:05:12,850 --> 00:05:15,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kyoya is here.</font>

79
00:05:15,500 --> 00:05:18,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Archon was right.</font>

80
00:05:19,420 --> 00:05:26,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we use her, we can revive XENOS 
without relying on Earth.</font>

81
00:05:26,970 --> 00:05:29,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I am Kyoya of SI-VIS.</i></font>

82
00:05:30,520 --> 00:05:32,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll make sure everyone survives!</i></font>

83
00:05:32,940 --> 00:05:34,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How fortuitous.</font>

84
00:05:34,580 --> 00:05:37,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With Earth and 
the new Diva on our side,</font>

85
00:05:37,010 --> 00:05:40,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">our revival will be a
 hundred years closer.</font>

86
00:05:42,210 --> 00:05:44,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Medea-san, are these...?</font>

87
00:05:44,860 --> 00:05:47,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, the people of XENOS.</font>

88
00:05:48,170 --> 00:05:51,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They placed their hope of resurrection 
in us and went to sleep.</font>

89
00:06:00,460 --> 00:06:01,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A Mirage?!</font>

90
00:06:01,690 --> 00:06:03,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the heck is that?</font>

91
00:06:06,830 --> 00:06:07,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A trap?</font>

92
00:06:07,470 --> 00:06:11,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No. This is most likely 
a trap as well as a chance.</font>

93
00:06:12,640 --> 00:06:18,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's only one XENOS left who 
would do something dramatic like this.</font>

94
00:06:18,400 --> 00:06:20,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know! It's that pervy old man!</font>

95
00:06:23,860 --> 00:06:29,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can no longer tell 
what Samael's true intention is.</font>

96
00:06:29,620 --> 00:06:36,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it feels to me like it is 
very personal and impulsive.</font>

97
00:06:36,630 --> 00:06:38,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He wants to fight us?</font>

98
00:06:39,190 --> 00:06:43,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure he's waiting for us with 
a hostage of one plus billions of people.</font>

99
00:06:43,860 --> 00:06:45,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mean Nagi and...</font>

100
00:06:45,520 --> 00:06:47,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The lives of the earthlings.</font>

101
00:06:47,890 --> 00:06:52,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we crush this Mirage, then the Mirages 
on Earth should disappear as well.</font>

102
00:06:52,890 --> 00:06:56,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It wouldn't make sense to
put on a show like this otherwise.</font>

103
00:06:56,900 --> 00:06:59,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then all we do is to take the bait 
with everything we've got.</font>

104
00:07:00,210 --> 00:07:02,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone, just do it as usual, okay?</font>

105
00:07:05,080 --> 00:07:06,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Until the live concert begins...</font>

106
00:07:08,040 --> 00:07:12,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or until those 25 cities disappear, 
we've got 15 minutes left.</font>

107
00:07:13,500 --> 00:07:16,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What emotions are you going through?</font>

108
00:07:26,650 --> 00:07:28,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you all right, everyone?!</font>

109
00:07:30,340 --> 00:07:31,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Medea-san!</font>

110
00:07:31,420 --> 00:07:33,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now's not the time to worry about me!</font>

111
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:36,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Telling him that is pointless.</font>

112
00:07:36,560 --> 00:07:40,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He can't even protect himself, 
but he tries to protect everyone.</font>

113
00:07:40,930 --> 00:07:42,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's mean.</font>

114
00:07:48,260 --> 00:07:49,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's...</font>

115
00:07:52,530 --> 00:07:55,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A revived cyborg?</font>

116
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:57,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As expected of the pervy old man.</font>

117
00:07:57,080 --> 00:07:59,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I knew he had bad taste, but this is peak.</font>

118
00:08:03,350 --> 00:08:04,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here goes our all-out attack.</font>

119
00:08:05,070 --> 00:08:06,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone, let's go!</font>

120
00:08:08,350 --> 00:08:10,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, that's not it!</font>

121
00:08:10,730 --> 00:08:12,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's just do our usual.</font>

122
00:08:13,780 --> 00:08:16,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leave this to us and keep going!</font>

123
00:08:16,910 --> 00:08:18,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Soji, μ...</font>

124
00:08:18,900 --> 00:08:21,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a race against time!</font>

125
00:08:21,030 --> 00:08:24,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our combat power won't change 
that much if you aren't here!</font>

126
00:08:24,720 --> 00:08:25,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

127
00:08:25,750 --> 00:08:29,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think you'd be better off 
if we weren't with you.</font>

128
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:34,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I bet there'll be a full display 
of embarrassing lines like,</font>

129
00:08:34,970 --> 00:08:37,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Give back my Nagi, 
you scoundrel!" and whatnot.</font>

130
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:42,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, come on! You guys 
never listen to me!</font>

131
00:08:42,970 --> 00:08:45,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, I'll go do my solo.</font>

132
00:08:45,170 --> 00:08:46,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But we'll do the next
song with the full cast!</font>

133
00:08:47,830 --> 00:08:49,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're going, too!</font>

134
00:08:49,490 --> 00:08:52,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please. I need you to back him up.</font>

135
00:08:56,750 --> 00:09:00,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Make sure our leader looks cool, will you?</font>

136
00:09:01,690 --> 00:09:04,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"Our leader"?</i></font>

137
00:09:05,070 --> 00:09:07,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is that how a leader should be?</i></font>

138
00:09:09,330 --> 00:09:12,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Orphe led and guided 
everyone from the front.</i></font>

139
00:09:12,540 --> 00:09:14,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He produced results on his own.</i></font>

140
00:09:15,470 --> 00:09:18,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He never showed his weakness.</i></font>

141
00:09:20,510 --> 00:09:21,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But that boy...</i></font>

142
00:09:28,530 --> 00:09:32,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, but leave the princess 
and I alone, will you?</font>

143
00:09:32,600 --> 00:09:34,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've done your bidding so far, haven't I?</font>

144
00:09:43,800 --> 00:09:45,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yo, Princess.</font>

145
00:09:47,230 --> 00:09:48,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kyoya is coming.</font>

146
00:09:49,230 --> 00:09:53,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup, your knight will arrive soon.</font>

147
00:09:56,500 --> 00:09:58,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To kill me.</font>

148
00:09:59,060 --> 00:10:00,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're wrong.</font>

149
00:10:00,540 --> 00:10:03,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kyoya won't kill or hate.</font>

150
00:10:04,040 --> 00:10:07,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's a true hero who saves everyone.</font>

151
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:11,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I kinda need him 
to fight me, you know?</font>

152
00:10:12,190 --> 00:10:16,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Otherwise, there's no 
growing stronger, you see?</font>

153
00:10:18,720 --> 00:10:20,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nagi!</font>

154
00:10:20,650 --> 00:10:23,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome to my homeland!</font>

155
00:10:23,190 --> 00:10:26,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Diva's Knight 
and successor of Orphe!</font>

156
00:10:26,470 --> 00:10:27,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nagi!</font>

157
00:10:27,460 --> 00:10:28,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kyoya!</font>

158
00:10:28,750 --> 00:10:30,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Set Nagi free!</font>

159
00:10:30,070 --> 00:10:34,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you want your princess back, 
try and stop this Mirage.</font>

160
00:10:34,630 --> 00:10:37,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you manage to do it, 
I'll give you a reward!</font>

161
00:10:37,810 --> 00:10:42,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll stop every Mirage 
on Earth, not just here.</font>

162
00:10:43,110 --> 00:10:45,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because its core is right here.</font>

163
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:47,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You must stop this, Samael!</font>

164
00:10:48,150 --> 00:10:50,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You touched her power, didn't you?</font>

165
00:10:50,420 --> 00:10:52,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then you must have realized</font>

166
00:10:52,500 --> 00:10:56,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that there's a way for both 
XENOS and the earthlings</font>

167
00:10:56,060 --> 00:10:58,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to survive without taking Earth!</font>

168
00:11:00,400 --> 00:11:02,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Apollo, Orphe, you...</font>

169
00:11:03,590 --> 00:11:07,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why can't you be a bit more flexible?</font>

170
00:11:07,670 --> 00:11:11,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who cares about the future 
of the human species?</font>

171
00:11:11,240 --> 00:11:12,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Samael!</font>

172
00:11:13,750 --> 00:11:15,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You must have known...</font>

173
00:11:16,990 --> 00:11:21,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What we're doing to take Earth.</font>

174
00:11:22,650 --> 00:11:25,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What we have done.</font>

175
00:11:28,950 --> 00:11:35,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our friends who entrusted the future 
of XENOS to us and went to sleep...</font>

176
00:11:36,110 --> 00:11:40,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our friends who went to sleep, 
believing that they'd wake up one day...</font>

177
00:11:42,140 --> 00:11:46,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've consumed their lives to be here.</font>

178
00:11:48,940 --> 00:11:52,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's why... That's exactly why!</i></font>

179
00:11:52,060 --> 00:11:55,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Now might be our chance 
to stop the cycle of loss.</i></font>

180
00:11:55,820 --> 00:11:59,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is a one-in-a-million chance!</i></font>

181
00:12:00,660 --> 00:12:01,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right.</font>

182
00:12:04,390 --> 00:12:08,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should stick to your beliefs, Medea.</font>

183
00:12:09,680 --> 00:12:12,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I will do the same.</font>

184
00:12:14,380 --> 00:12:16,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why, Samael?!</font>

185
00:12:19,230 --> 00:12:21,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that all you have to say?</font>

186
00:12:21,050 --> 00:12:23,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is Lord Apollo's opinion?!</font>

187
00:12:23,050 --> 00:12:27,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't imagine him 
tolerating your reckless behavior!</font>

188
00:12:28,130 --> 00:12:32,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">True, Apollo probably wouldn't 
condone my <i>purpose</i>.</font>

189
00:12:33,210 --> 00:12:39,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But he'd allow me to destroy 
SI-VIS to gain Earth.</font>

190
00:12:39,650 --> 00:12:41,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's how he is.</font>

191
00:12:42,230 --> 00:12:43,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That can't be...!</font>

192
00:12:44,390 --> 00:12:47,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you don't have anyone 
to protect, find someone.</font>

193
00:12:47,650 --> 00:12:50,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get to know someone well enough 
that they're no longer a stranger!</font>

194
00:12:50,830 --> 00:12:53,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you hear that, Medea?</font>

195
00:12:53,230 --> 00:12:54,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How about you?</font>

196
00:12:55,130 --> 00:13:00,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You lost Orphe, the only love you had.
Can you say the same thing?</font>

197
00:13:01,150 --> 00:13:05,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Orphe might be gone, 
but his wishes will live on forever.</font>

198
00:13:06,600 --> 00:13:10,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For people he's never met, 
for people from different cultures...</font>

199
00:13:11,040 --> 00:13:13,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and even for people 
who are yet to be born,</font>

200
00:13:13,970 --> 00:13:16,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">he served his mission and gave his life.</font>

201
00:13:17,400 --> 00:13:20,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to be someone like that as well.</font>

202
00:13:20,950 --> 00:13:21,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

203
00:13:24,490 --> 00:13:30,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aren't you blessed to be able to live on 
with just the memories of loved ones?</font>

204
00:13:31,480 --> 00:13:35,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, you're just caught up in a curse.</font>

205
00:13:37,510 --> 00:13:39,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a foolish way to live!</font>

206
00:13:42,340 --> 00:13:44,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will stop you, Samael!</font>

207
00:13:44,440 --> 00:13:47,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nagi and I, with the song of SI-VIS!</font>

208
00:13:56,150 --> 00:13:57,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go ahead and try.</font>

209
00:13:57,930 --> 00:14:02,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come at me with your little live 
concert, a farce you all believe in!</font>

210
00:14:03,390 --> 00:14:06,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Even the pain I locked up</i></font>

211
00:14:06,700 --> 00:14:10,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I threw it away with a trembling heart</i></font>

212
00:14:07,410 --> 00:14:09,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Otherwise, it is the end of humanity!</i></font>

213
00:14:10,260 --> 00:14:13,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Silence is swirling</i></font>

214
00:14:10,790 --> 00:14:14,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You must hate me. 
You must want to kill me.</i></font>

215
00:14:13,790 --> 00:14:17,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}A breath signals the beginning</i></font>

216
00:14:14,670 --> 00:14:17,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Kick me with the intent to kill.</i></font>

217
00:14:17,040 --> 00:14:19,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Punch and pierce me with your fists!</i></font>

218
00:14:17,690 --> 00:14:21,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Sounds come flooding back, 
illuminating the darkness</i></font>

219
00:14:19,820 --> 00:14:21,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If not, then die!</i></font>

220
00:14:21,200 --> 00:14:24,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Our dissonance swells</i></font>

221
00:14:21,890 --> 00:14:26,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Give your life to XENOS and disappear!</i></font>

222
00:14:24,680 --> 00:14:31,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The dreary world spreads 
as far as eyes can see</i></font>

223
00:14:26,360 --> 00:14:27,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the hell?!</font>

224
00:14:28,110 --> 00:14:29,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You die!</font>

225
00:14:29,190 --> 00:14:31,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this guy for real?! Shut the hell up!</font>

226
00:14:31,120 --> 00:14:32,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kill him!</font>

227
00:14:32,380 --> 00:14:34,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get lost! Get lost! Get lost!</font>

228
00:14:33,530 --> 00:14:37,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Run through to the ends of the Earth</i></font>

229
00:14:37,110 --> 00:14:39,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Idea is rising rapidly.</font>

230
00:14:37,780 --> 00:14:40,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Arrows pour down endlessly</i></font>

231
00:14:39,830 --> 00:14:42,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Three hundred thousand, 
three hundred fifty thousand...</font>

232
00:14:40,610 --> 00:14:44,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}But we let out thunderous roars</i></font>

233
00:14:42,890 --> 00:14:45,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">B-But this is...</font>

234
00:14:44,020 --> 00:14:54,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Strike a chord that fuels clenched fists</i></font>

235
00:14:50,430 --> 00:14:51,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take this!</font>

236
00:14:53,780 --> 00:14:54,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What was that?</font>

237
00:14:57,390 --> 00:15:01,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like you're ready 
to kill me, earthling!</font>

238
00:15:01,940 --> 00:15:04,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">N-No, that wasn't...!</font>

239
00:15:04,840 --> 00:15:18,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Kill him! Kill him! Kill him! Kill him!</i></font>

240
00:15:13,050 --> 00:15:16,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Our fate stands in front of us</i></font>

241
00:15:16,380 --> 00:15:19,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}All we can do is to tackle it head-on</i></font>

242
00:15:19,180 --> 00:15:20,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Stop it, please!</i></font>

243
00:15:19,740 --> 00:15:23,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Now set your heart ablaze 
until there's nothing left</i></font>

244
00:15:20,710 --> 00:15:22,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This isn't... This is not...</i></font>

245
00:15:22,360 --> 00:15:24,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Not the voices we wanted to hear!</i></font>

246
00:15:23,110 --> 00:15:28,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Who rings the bell of blessings?</i></font>

247
00:15:24,350 --> 00:15:26,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I want you to enjoy our performance!</i></font>

248
00:15:26,560 --> 00:15:29,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Don't get hyped up 
about people getting hurt!</i></font>

249
00:15:28,800 --> 00:15:35,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Souls, resonance, an impulse 
that pierces our brains</i></font>

250
00:15:35,760 --> 00:15:39,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Earthlings, XENOS...</font>

251
00:15:35,820 --> 00:15:43,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Tears, the surge of pain 
rising in a blink of an eye</i></font>

252
00:15:40,180 --> 00:15:42,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you both lost.</font>

253
00:15:42,300 --> 00:15:45,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I... I alone am the winner!</font>

254
00:15:43,630 --> 00:15:49,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Push away the unsteady mist and shout</i></font>

255
00:15:48,300 --> 00:15:53,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now you will kill until 
both sides are destroyed!</font>

256
00:15:53,100 --> 00:15:57,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Sing out loud at the top of your lungs</i></font>

257
00:15:56,220 --> 00:16:00,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's the ultimate gift from me,</font>

258
00:15:57,340 --> 00:16:01,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Because words will turn into 
weapons wrapped in passion</i></font>

259
00:16:00,400 --> 00:16:04,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">who lost family, friends, 
everyone I've ever loved!</font>

260
00:16:01,610 --> 00:16:03,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Go without hesitation</i></font>

261
00:16:03,520 --> 00:16:13,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Let the lives of all of us here 
shine brightly</i></font>

262
00:16:04,710 --> 00:16:06,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take it!</font>

263
00:16:06,890 --> 00:16:08,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Medea-san!</font>

264
00:16:08,010 --> 00:16:09,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please cut off the cheers from Earth!</font>

265
00:16:09,900 --> 00:16:13,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But the only reason 
we can stand against Samael—</font>

266
00:16:13,670 --> 00:16:15,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we win like this, then we've lost!</font>

267
00:16:18,430 --> 00:16:19,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop it, Samael!</font>

268
00:16:20,340 --> 00:16:22,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to save them all!</font>

269
00:16:22,580 --> 00:16:25,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not just the people 
on Earth, but XENOS, too.</font>

270
00:16:25,420 --> 00:16:28,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you should be saved as well!</font>

271
00:16:28,970 --> 00:16:32,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Stormy winds, freezing fingers</i></font>

272
00:16:30,430 --> 00:16:33,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that so? I'm the opposite.</font>

273
00:16:32,820 --> 00:16:39,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Running through the land 
that was torn apart</i></font>

274
00:16:33,920 --> 00:16:35,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to destroy them all.</font>

275
00:16:36,260 --> 00:16:40,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The people on Earth, XENOS...</font>

276
00:16:39,730 --> 00:16:48,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Two wishes that will never cross forever</i></font>

277
00:16:42,550 --> 00:16:45,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And the one who deserves 
to be destroyed more than anyone...</font>

278
00:16:47,910 --> 00:16:52,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is me, who can't do anything 
but get revenge!</font>

279
00:16:48,090 --> 00:16:53,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The color of darkness eats away the light</i></font>

280
00:16:53,460 --> 00:17:00,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Oh, the back of my throat 
is completely dried up in misery</i></font>

281
00:16:53,570 --> 00:16:59,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Samael. The weakling who was consumed
by hatred because of his kindness.</font>

282
00:17:00,280 --> 00:17:04,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your heart that craves
destruction will save XENOS.</font>

283
00:17:00,430 --> 00:17:07,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}On the stage of pure darkness, 
heartbeats resonate</i></font>

284
00:17:06,050 --> 00:17:11,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If your loved ones are not among 
the ones who get revived,</font>

285
00:17:07,420 --> 00:17:11,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}With bated breath, it starts moving</i></font>

286
00:17:11,830 --> 00:17:16,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it just means you were out of luck.</font>

287
00:17:11,870 --> 00:17:16,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Toward the time that leads to the future</i></font>

288
00:17:16,600 --> 00:17:19,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have to connect with Earth!</font>

289
00:17:19,190 --> 00:17:22,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}As loud as it can be</i></font>

290
00:17:19,220 --> 00:17:20,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not now.</font>

291
00:17:21,130 --> 00:17:23,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What we need to rely on is not hate!</font>

292
00:17:24,230 --> 00:17:27,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Friends, comrades, 
people who live in the same world...</font>

293
00:17:26,060 --> 00:17:30,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Let our song pierce through</i></font>

294
00:17:27,360 --> 00:17:31,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even those who live in different worlds... 
We need kindness to protect everyone!</font>

295
00:17:31,950 --> 00:17:35,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}At the bottom of the desolate heart</i></font>

296
00:17:32,130 --> 00:17:34,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But that's nowhere to be found right now!</font>

297
00:17:35,410 --> 00:17:41,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Even if wounds and scars 
may forever leave marks</i></font>

298
00:17:41,540 --> 00:17:48,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}It all makes up who I am</i></font>

299
00:17:44,620 --> 00:17:46,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A Chariot?</font>

300
00:17:46,630 --> 00:17:47,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry for the delay!</font>

301
00:17:47,810 --> 00:17:49,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">June-kun?!</font>

302
00:17:49,170 --> 00:17:51,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not just him, got it?!</font>

303
00:17:50,710 --> 00:17:54,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Let me hear the cheers…</i></font>

304
00:17:52,590 --> 00:17:54,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your solo part is over!</font>

305
00:17:56,530 --> 00:17:59,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why? Why?</font>

306
00:17:58,750 --> 00:18:04,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Led by the stars</i></font>

307
00:17:59,180 --> 00:18:08,860
<font size="20"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="13"><font color="#a69b88">Team Formation for
the Next Concert</font></font></font></font>

308
00:17:59,180 --> 00:18:08,860
<font size="20"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="13"><font color="#867d6e">Center!</font></font></font></font>

309
00:17:59,180 --> 00:18:08,860
<font size="20"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="13"><font color="#867d6e">Kyoya</font></font></font></font>

310
00:17:59,180 --> 00:18:08,860
<font size="20"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="13"><font color="#867d6e">Soji</font></font></font></font>

311
00:17:59,180 --> 00:18:08,860
<font size="20"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="13"><font color="#867d6e">June</font></font></font></font>

312
00:17:59,610 --> 00:18:04,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did he give his and
Lukos's Pandora to SI-VIS?</font>

313
00:18:04,500 --> 00:18:07,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. I received it.</font>

314
00:18:05,330 --> 00:18:11,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Staying close, I feel your warmth</i></font>

315
00:18:07,390 --> 00:18:09,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What did you do, Krios?!</font>

316
00:18:10,360 --> 00:18:12,110
<font size="20"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font size="13"><font color="#771230">{\an8}This is Nagi's masterpiece!



Write some awesome music for it!</font></font></b></font></font>

317
00:18:10,360 --> 00:18:15,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you form a bond with an actual 
earthling that's not even Orphe?!</font>

318
00:18:12,310 --> 00:18:18,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Passing on love, united through hearts</i></font>

319
00:18:16,230 --> 00:18:21,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you seriously willing to follow the 
immature aspirations of these brats?!</font>

320
00:18:18,690 --> 00:18:24,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Turning it into a mighty power</i></font>

321
00:18:25,580 --> 00:18:29,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Our resolution won't waver</i></font>

322
00:18:29,300 --> 00:18:32,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Bet on everything you have</i></font>

323
00:18:30,550 --> 00:18:34,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You're imperfect 
and not enough in every aspect.</i></font>

324
00:18:32,680 --> 00:18:39,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Now draw a breath</i></font>

325
00:18:34,460 --> 00:18:40,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But that's why everyone 
can't help but rally around you.</i></font>

326
00:18:40,640 --> 00:18:43,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Let it resonate 
and resonate forever and ever</i></font>

327
00:18:43,000 --> 00:18:46,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Being imperfect is your biggest advantage.</i></font>

328
00:18:43,930 --> 00:18:47,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Go on, go on to the unknown world</i></font>

329
00:18:47,980 --> 00:18:53,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Reach out your hand 
and the world will expand</i></font>

330
00:18:50,460 --> 00:18:52,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So that's the kind of leader you are.</i></font>

331
00:18:53,610 --> 00:18:56,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is going to... end it!</font>

332
00:18:53,970 --> 00:18:57,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Sing and sing forever and ever</i></font>

333
00:18:56,630 --> 00:18:59,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">SI-VIS!</font>

334
00:18:57,310 --> 00:19:01,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Until our wishes reach you</i></font>

335
00:19:01,120 --> 00:19:11,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}We'll play the melody of hope</i></font>

336
00:19:01,400 --> 00:19:02,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Samael!</i></font>

337
00:19:03,000 --> 00:19:04,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Come back to us!</i></font>

338
00:19:16,830 --> 00:19:18,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For me to be defeated...</font>

339
00:19:19,900 --> 00:19:23,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and to make them stronger was my purpose.</font>

340
00:19:24,840 --> 00:19:26,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So why...?</font>

341
00:19:28,960 --> 00:19:31,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why am I frustrated?</font>

342
00:19:33,400 --> 00:19:36,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Mirages over the 25 
cities are all disappearing!</font>

343
00:19:39,580 --> 00:19:43,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Not only me, but he moved Krios as well.</i></font>

344
00:19:44,160 --> 00:19:48,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It wasn't just Kyoya-san, 
but all of SI-VIS.</i></font>

345
00:19:49,140 --> 00:19:51,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's a group that's nothing more 
than a bunch of friends</i></font>

346
00:19:51,710 --> 00:19:54,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>led by an inexperienced leader.</i></font>

347
00:19:55,170 --> 00:19:59,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But they've done
what Orphe never could.</i></font>

348
00:20:00,590 --> 00:20:04,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Orphe, did you foresee this?</i></font>

349
00:20:05,010 --> 00:20:06,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Were you hoping for this outcome?</i></font>

350
00:20:07,150 --> 00:20:09,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No, probably not.</i></font>

351
00:20:09,920 --> 00:20:14,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Knowing you, you were probably 
trying to protect them on your own.</i></font>

352
00:20:15,700 --> 00:20:23,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But your overeagerness created 
a new savior who isn't overeager.</i></font>

353
00:20:24,620 --> 00:20:27,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's all thanks to you, Orphe.</i></font>

354
00:20:28,980 --> 00:20:35,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'd imagine this isn't the result 
you were hoping for, though.</i></font>

