 / In the musical stave</i></font>

358
00:21:00,310 --> 00:21:02,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}WOW, I let my feelings play
 / I hid my feelings</i></font>

359
00:21:02,780 --> 00:21:05,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}My bright future / My pitiful past</i></font>

360
00:21:05,720 --> 00:21:08,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}WOW, started to shine</i></font>

361
00:21:08,190 --> 00:21:10,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Unparalleled / Challenges ahead but</i></font>

362
00:21:10,970 --> 00:21:13,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}With a smile on my face
 / I'll embrace them</i></font>

363
00:21:13,570 --> 00:21:18,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I feel like I can even change 
the world with you</i></font>

364
00:21:18,890 --> 00:21:21,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}(3, 2, 1, Singing over)</i></font>

365
00:21:21,550 --> 00:21:26,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Intertwining harmony (Harmony)</i></font>

366
00:21:26,610 --> 00:21:32,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I wouldn't have believed in miracles alone</i></font>

367
00:21:32,620 --> 00:21:37,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}This breathless heartbeat (Heart Beat)</i></font>

368
00:21:37,440 --> 00:21:42,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I'll let it resonate in
 the night sky with my voice</i></font>

369
00:21:42,690 --> 00:21:50,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}My... our dream at full blast</i></font>

370
00:21:54,310 --> 00:21:57,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Singing over, forever</i></font>

371
00:21:57,210 --> 00:22:00,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Lan lan la la la</i></font>

372
00:22:15,410 --> 00:22:17,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will stop Lord Apollo.</font>

373
00:22:18,070 --> 00:22:20,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's the only one left.</font>

374
00:22:20,220 --> 00:22:23,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And there's no one who
 supports him anymore.</font>

375
00:22:23,440 --> 00:22:25,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should join us and—</font>

376
00:22:25,340 --> 00:22:26,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's too late.</font>

377
00:22:26,810 --> 00:22:28,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That is not true!</font>

378
00:22:29,100 --> 00:22:31,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why don't we work together?</font>

379
00:22:31,570 --> 00:22:38,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To find a way to save this planet, 
Earth, and all the people we love.</font>

380
00:22:40,200 --> 00:22:45,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Unfortunately, I've already 
made a deal with the devil.</font>

381
00:22:46,690 --> 00:22:49,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In exchange for the power 
to destroy everything,</font>

382
00:22:50,260 --> 00:22:53,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I promised to devote 
everything to the Diva.</font>

383
00:22:53,600 --> 00:22:56,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Apollo is not an absolute evil!</font>

384
00:22:56,860 --> 00:23:01,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He is simply obsessed with saving XENOS.</font>

385
00:23:02,410 --> 00:23:03,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Apollo?</font>

386
00:23:05,710 --> 00:23:07,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right.</font>

387
00:23:08,510 --> 00:23:11,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't know true evil, do you?</font>

388
00:23:12,350 --> 00:23:15,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">True evil?</font>

389
00:23:19,590 --> 00:23:20,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Samael!</font>

390
00:23:21,360 --> 00:23:24,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Farewell, Medea.</font>

391
00:23:26,430 --> 00:23:27,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kyoya!</font>

392
00:23:28,760 --> 00:23:30,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nagi!</font>

